^ 化學親和力：http://jpkc.zju.edu.cn/k/406/courseware/course/chap14/55.htm 浙江大學。
^ Prigogine & Defay, p. 38; Prigogine, p. 24


Chemical Thermodynamics - University of North Carolina
Chemical energetics（Introduction to thermodynamics and the First Law）
Thermodynamics of chemical equilibrium（Entropy, Second Law and free energy）

深入閱讀[編輯]

Herbert B. Callen. Thermodynamics. Wiley & Sons. The clearest account of the logical foundations of the subject. 1960. ISBN 0471130354.  Library of Congress Catalog No. 60-5597
Ilya Prigogine & R. Defay, translated by D.H. Everett; Chapter IV. Chemical Thermodynamics. Longmans, Green & Co. Exceptionally clear on the logical foundations as applied to chemistry; includes non-equilibrium thermodynamics. 1954. 
Ilya Prigogine. Thermodynamics of Irreversible Processes, 3rd ed.. Interscience: John Wiley & Sons. A simple, concise monograph explaining all the basic ideas. 1967.  Library of Congress Catalog No. 67-29540
E.A. Guggenheim. Thermodynamics: An Advanced Treatment for Chemists and Physicists, 5th ed.. North Holland; John Wiley & Sons (Interscience). A remarkably astute treatise. 1967.  Library of Congress Catalog No. 67-20003
Th. De Donder. Bull. Ac. Roy. Belg. (Cl. Sc.) (5). 1922, 7: 197, 205.  缺少或|title=為空 (幫助)









